/**********************************************************************************************************************
**		Name: [RSU].[spAutoGen_UserTypes_UPDATE]
**		Desc: Autogenerated SPROC to UPDATE a row for [RSU].[UserTypes]
**		Auth: ANDRES E. SOSA
